ğŸ What is Debugging?

**Debugging** is the process of **finding, understanding, and fixing errors (bugs)** in code.

ğŸ“Œ Bugs can be:

* Syntax errors
* Runtime errors
* Logical errors

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ§ª Common JavaScript Errors

1ï¸âƒ£ Syntax Error

```js
if (x === 10 {   // missing )
```

ğŸ“Œ Code will not run

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

2ï¸âƒ£ Runtime Error

```js
console.log(a); // a is not defined
```

ğŸ“Œ Occurs while program is running

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

3ï¸âƒ£ Logical Error

```js
let sum = 10 * 5; // should be +
```

ğŸ“Œ Program runs but gives wrong output

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ§  Debugging Tools (Very Important â­)

